===Etymology===
From [[w:Dharuk|Dharuk]] (Aboriginal language) ''[[gula]]'' or ''[[gulawany]]''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A tree-dwelling [[marsupial]] that resembles a small [[bear]] with a broad head, large ears and sharp claws, mainly found in eastern Australia.

====Scientific names====
